2e8bc36f3bb6c5ea","tid":2193732,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"688f6db63363f5f25ea91f94a8c49fe0e82f5ea6","tid":2193732,"uid":137604,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"407875bb964e5a09de902b6e9c16b220715933b6","tid":2193732,"uid":48234,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">老鳳認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連登日報&mdash;支持獨裁政權者，無權享有言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNv9jui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNv9jui.jpg&h=2d820456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問R730(狗隻#137604)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2111627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2111627</a><br />\n此狗隻奶共證據:<br />\n出言侮辱同路人，近日又留言指「聽到仲有人講831，真係好尷尬」。<br />\n建議而家即刻係各大屈臣氏大叫政府無能 馬上封關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eOKtbT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eOKtbT</a><br />\n太子站幕門突然碎裂  玻璃跌入路軌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/atgGEHV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/atgGEHV</a><br />\n<br />\n懷疑此帳號原擁有者可能已經被殺,以前反CCTVB,而家做CCTVB打手<br />\n睇CCTVB死全家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/794788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/794788</a><br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n此狗隻為沙皮狗分身明顯證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,明確承認開分身<br />\n<br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/GpbQh7RN/YOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FGpbQh7RN%2FYOU.jpg&h=eacd9956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成撚日話老鳳洗板,梗係啦,你啲罪證咁撚多,你出現已經等於迫老鳳洗板<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著他笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"6c3da97d6a7cfa1684c221f440aea3ece8294498","tid":2193732,"uid":92299,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd0a6cc2f9d6530b46b6b3aa03c20ae701e347de","tid":2193732,"uid":17799,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"戰爭狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:47:08.000Z","msg":"食黃店同買蘋果都可以係時代革命嘅時候，仲有咩係無可能？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ef3ff5fe396dc6ab45aca8727c94d327b74dbe","tid":2193732,"uid":4